  "text": "Like most financial return series, data in foreign exchange markets also exhibits some degree of autocorrelation and volatility clustering referring to values of Q (16) and Q2 [CITATION_1] . For the sake of deliberation, specific properties such as nonnormality and the nature of tail-thickness can also be directly confirmed through the Q-Q plot in figure 2 .",
